-- UniCredit Preparing Sale of Seven-Year Covered Bonds in Euros, Banker Says
-- B y   S o n j a   C h e u n g
-- 2010-10-04T07:49:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/unicredit-to-sell-1-billion-euros-of-seven-year-covered-bonds.html
UniCredit SpA plans to sell 1 billion
euros of seven-year covered bonds, according to a banker
involved in the deal.  Banca IMI SpA, Commerzbank AG, Natixis and UBS AG are
helping UniCredit manage the sale.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonja Cheung in London at 
